367
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:59,100
Bohaté Dievča sa nakoniec stretla
s mamou.

368
00:32:59,890 --> 00:33:01,390
Vďaka Bohu.

369
00:33:01,390 --> 00:33:06,110
Možno budeš sklamaný,
ale neplakala som.

370
00:33:07,520 --> 00:33:10,160
